snippet.title: The Lemmings Chronicles / All New World of Lemmings
snippet.description: The Lemmings Chronicles is a puzzle platform game developed by DMA Design and published by Psygnosis in 1994. Like in its prequels, the goal is to bring as many lemmings as possible safely to the exit.
